---
title: Tandoori Lentil Bunless Burger with Oven Fries & Cucumber Raita
description: Mix up your burger menu with this bunless lentil version. The patty comes together quickly and with a gentle spice from tandoori paste, it’s full of flavour. With all the fresh burger trimmings, including a creamy yoghurt and sweet mango chutney, plus baked potato chips, this is a satisifying plate of goodness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5beba63f30006c1b7a608112-095577ee.jpg
